    "content": "import time
import logging

class EvolutionSystem:
    def __init__(self, initial_state, evolve_function, evaluate_function, config):
        self.state = initial_state
        self.evolve_function = evolve_function
        self.evaluate_function = evaluate_function
        self.config = config
        self.logger = logging.getLogger(__name__)
        self.logger.setLevel(logging.INFO)

    def run(self):
        start_time = time.time()
        self.logger.info(f"Evolution started at: {start_time}")
        
        generation = 0
        while generation < self.config.max_generations:
            generation_start_time = time.time()
            self.logger.info(f"Generation {generation} started at: {generation_start_time}")

            # Evolve
            self.logger.info(f"Evolving state...")
            evolve_start_time = time.time()
            new_state = self.evolve_function(self.state, self.config)
            evolve_end_time = time.time()
            self.logger.info(f"Evolving state completed in {evolve_end_time - evolve_start_time} seconds")
            self.logger.debug(f"New state: {new_state}")

            # Evaluate
            self.logger.info(f"Evaluating state...")
            evaluate_start_time = time.time()
            evaluation = self.evaluate_function(new_state)
            evaluate_end_time = time.time()
            self.logger.info(f"Evaluating state completed in {evaluate_end_time - evaluate_start_time} seconds")
            self.logger.info(f"Evaluation score: {evaluation}")

            # Update state
            self.state = new_state
            self.logger.info(f"State updated.")
            self.logger.debug(f"Current state: {self.state}")
            
            generation_end_time = time.time()
            self.logger.info(f"Generation {generation} completed in {generation_end_time - generation_start_time} seconds")
            generation += 1

        end_time = time.time()
        self.logger.info(f"Evolution completed at: {end_time}")
        self.logger.info(f"Total evolution time: {end_time - start_time} seconds")
        return self.state"
  }
